"*Dečki* su išli u školu." (The boys went to school.)
"*Dečki* su se igrali." (The boys were playing.)
"Mama je *dečkima* kupila sladoled." (Mom bought an ice cream for the boys.)
"*Dečki* su se družili u parku." (The boys were hanging out in the park.)
"*Dečki* su se smejali." (The boys were laughing.)